org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute

Class PaAttributeValueNumericVersionBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pa.attribute.PaAttributeValueNumericVersionBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImAttributeValueBuilder, TransmissionObjectBuilder<ImAttributeValue>, PaAttributeValueNumericVersionBuilder

    public class PaAttributeValueNumericVersionBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PaAttributeValueNumericVersionBuilder
    Builder to build an integrity measurement numeric version attribute value compliant to RFC 5792. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
